text: Does anyone have a recommendation for a good file sharing back up and online back up...have used drop box, box, and syncplicity in the past...and wondered if there were any other recommendations...
I've used <https://www.box.com/> before. But dropbox is still my favorite. There is microsoft onedrive as another alternative as well.
